tree fern
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a large fern having a trunk-like stem with fronds at the top. See also ponga, mamaku, wheki
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also fern tree
